'''Mostly Autumn''' is a British prog-rock band, with many songs based on [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien's]] works. In 2001 they released a concept album based on the [[The Lord of the Rings|Lord of the Rings]] trilogy, titled [[Music Inspired by the Lord of the Rings]].
